name: Planet Lapis Lazuli
description: Planet Lapis Lazuli is the planet of inner peace and freedom from negative thought. This planet activates the higher mind and enhances intellectual ability. Here inner truth is revealed, self awareness is promoted, and this knowledge is accepted. This planet provides relief of things that my have been suppressed and allows for them to surface; helping to diminish uncomfortable feelings and allows for self expression without holding back or compromising. It is here that deep communication of all kind is supported.
